{"tid":417832,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"細行既Travel Consultant 做唔做得過？","createTime":"2017-09-29T05:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T14:49:34.000Z","uid":150893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ff6fd23924eab79edf0c07c04e23fc0f9cf6df19","tid":417832,"uid":150893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n岩岩畢業搵工，去左間細行interview，做埋d tasks，成三個幾鐘先走得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後話比個offer我係萬二，返星期一到六，星期日輪流on call聽電話<br />\n個interviewer話叫我有定心理準備日日都要OT先.........<br />\n老闆話白紙OT就一定嫁啦，慢慢做落去就會上手.....<br />\n老闆話其他我白紙，請我係唔抵，但見我都好多旅遊經驗先比個機會我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我真係有興趣，但見呢間行成日都keep住請人.....怕有伏<br />\n有無巴絲可以分享下經驗？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d999ec13f0cd12992ed6575fe5e48cfca818b54","tid":417832,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"中學畢業就做<br />\n大學大專唔好做"},{"pid":"75c64e6a175ca2a243085a303363e72261090749","tid":417832,"uid":63,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:06:14.000Z","msg":"又星期六又星期日又3粒鐘task又ot 先得12k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7de7444bba235fd7ccf0b1446f637c5e6ca027","tid":417832,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:07:14.000Z","msg":"有冇最低工資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33b3c968cedee17f789e7f795903f6fa5b928f5","tid":417832,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n同做狗無分別"},{"pid":"3936511ce2861866069629f018c54f24cfe1b5b5","tid":417832,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"12K <br />\n6日<br />\n日日OT<br />\n咁既OFFER都做除非樓主你自問係隻狗啦"},{"pid":"a39f30ae41d088b83b32184a54f3374450e0ea72","tid":417832,"uid":150893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學畢業就做<br />\n大學大專唔好做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老闆話比多左我。。。。。我來回車程日日都要兩個半鐘<br />\n但身邊朋友都叫我捱下。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我係大專畢"},{"pid":"c7a960959e70aa9e596d00a53acbe6300c9e9443","tid":417832,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中學畢業就做<br />\n大學大專唔好做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老闆話比多左我。。。。。我來回車程日日都要兩個半鐘<br />\n但身邊朋友都叫我捱下。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我係大專畢</blockquote><br />\n咁既老細好極有限<br />\n佢實叫你捱架啦 你唔捱佢邊有得嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03dcfd50ad38eb8fff266d2e7b50eaafeec1145","tid":417832,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"唔好做 搵過第二行好過 辛苦得黎無價值"},{"pid":"a61998735b0080c98becec669f492ff89d3310cb","tid":417832,"uid":146431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"唔好做。<br />\n後生個班有人做到一年半載已經叫耐就知咩事喇"},{"pid":"fe5d6ec249c96265ed673b626ae5c52add9d8531","tid":417832,"uid":82818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"呢行做十年都冇20k，仲要返六日，咁都仲要諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe39b907f5fd30a1fc69bba2916ac4c65aa890c","tid":417832,"uid":63270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中學畢業就做<br />\n大學大專唔好做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老闆話比多左我。。。。。我來回車程日日都要兩個半鐘<br />\n但身邊朋友都叫我捱下。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我係大專畢</blockquote><br />\n唔好浪費自己青春 寧願花多少少時間搵過第二份好過"},{"pid":"6370521abd0e61384b142a54fac449641d5b4c20","tid":417832,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"跑數"},{"pid":"c0204c40cc8bfdb1663cf43b473b4b0e70906a10","tid":417832,"uid":128417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc